                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6226" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0307</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8987 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一山二虎，新旧难容——HL股份新项目建设的领导冲突困境</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Two leaders at odds, who will stay？——The dilemma of leadership conflict in new project construction of HL company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王崇锋，张耀东，周莉敏，刘丽庆，刘欣荣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛汉缆股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HL公司；“1+1”合作制度；组织冲突；组织权力与影响力；团队有效性；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HL Company; &quot;1+1&quot; Cooperation System; Organizational Conflict; Organizational Power and Influence; Team Effectiveness</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，国家出台多项环保政策法规促进电线电缆企业向“绿色、节能、环保”转型，低烟无卤材料由于性能稳定、低污染性等特征被认为是未来电缆材料的发展趋势。本案例聚焦于大型电缆企业HL公司低烟无卤电缆材料项目建设过程，以董事长收到的一封“投诉书”为引，通过情景再现的形式复盘了组织内部资历丰富的李冠丰（老李）和年轻有为的张运阳（小张）之间发生的矛盾冲突，梳理了“1+1”合作制度下，老派管理者与年轻管理者在处事方式、经验背景等方面的差异，以期为决策者如何解决组织内部冲突问题提供借鉴。案例为学员进行讨论和决策提供了必要的信息，学员可运用IPO模型、Thomas-Kilmann冲突管理风格框架等工具，深入探讨组织内部高管冲突的问题，系统学习组织冲突、组织权力与影响力、团队有效性等基本理论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, China has issued a number of environmental protection policies and regulations to promote the transformation of wire and cable enterprises to &quot;Green, Energy Saving and Environmental Protection&quot;. Low smoke and zero halogen materials are considered to be the development trend of cable materials due to their stable performance and low pollution. This case focuses on the construction process of the material project of HL Company. Based on a &quot;complaint&quot; received by the chairman of the board, the case reviews the conflicts between the well-qualified manager Li Guanfeng and the promising young-manager Zhang Yunyang, through the form of scene reconstruction. Under the &quot;1+1&quot; cooperation system, the differences between old-managers and young-managers in the way of doing things, experience and background, in order to provide reference for decision makers on how to solve internal conflicts in organizations. The case provides the necessary information for the students to discuss and make decisions. Students can use the IPO model and Thomas-Kilmann conflict management style framework and other tools to deeply explore the problem of executive conflict within the organization, and systematically learn the basic theories of organizational conflict, organizational power and influence.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《项目管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织冲突管理、组织领导力与决策、项目决策、项目组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-04</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
